Richter Approves 860 Forint Per Share Dividend, MTI Reports

-- B y   E d i t h   B a l a z s
-- 
2011-04-27T15:02:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/richter-approves-860-forint-per-share-dividend-mti-reports.html
Shareholders of Gedeon  Richter
Nyrt ., Hungary’s largest drugmaker, approved a company proposal
to pay out 860 forint per share in dividend from the 2010
profit, state news agency MTI said.  The remaining 48 billion forint ($266 million) net income,
calculated according Hungarian accounting standards, will be
transferred to the company’s profit reserves, MTI said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edith Balazs in Budapest at 
 ebalazs1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  